Submission:
Use your existing github project that you created in the lab session or create a new public
repository for your final project and submit the link to that repository in Brightspace. You
will not be submitting files on Brightspace for this assignment.
Copy the sample project to your repository and update to fit your project needs (naming,
documentation, python files/classes/functions, etc.).
Inside the doc/ folder place your progress report as a pdf file. Length of the report should
not be more than one page.
Update code of your project and demonstrate that you are able to obtain data from at least
one API data source. Add test code in your tests.py so we can run it too. Don’t forget to
update .gitignore, readme.md, requirements.txt .
